<code> git reset hard 31a936f </code> ( Shortcut jo commit reset krna ha us sa
pahla vala ke id dany ha )

<code>git reflog</code> Jo commit delete hua usky id mil jaya ge, ab seedha is
id ko reset man dal dan same procgre.

<code> git reset hard 31a936f </code> Same procgre jasa delete hua usy shortcut
sa vapis a gaya bus id change ke.

<code>git checkout head~1 </code> is case man hmara HEAD jo aik previous commit
ha us pr a jaya ga.

<code>git reset --hard head~2 </code> Sab sa common shortcut commit ko reset
krna ka apko yah mila ga.

<code> git revert 31a936f</code> commit ko revert krna ka shortcut ( Lakin Anuarg sir id da kr revert and reset krna prefer krta han ❤️)
<code> git revert head~1 </code> common shortcut apko mila ga revert krna ka head ka zaria. ( Basically usko aik commit id chayie, ab chha tum seedhy id da do ya head ka use kr kah commit ke id ko point krva do )

<code> git reset --hard head~1 </code> agr ghalty sa code revert kr dia to usko vapis lana ka shortcut ( same reset ka case ke trah ha ).

<code>git revert head~3..head</code> aik sa zayad commits ko aik sath revert krna ka Shortcut, Lakin is case man commits By-default bhe 3 create hon gan.

Powerful Shortcut kah hmara commit By-Default aik he create ho chha hm jitna he commits ka code aik sath delete kran👇🏿
<code>git revert --no-commit head~2..head</code> is case man hmary changings stage area man janya ge.
<code>git revert --abort</code> agr undo krna ha to isko use kro.
<code>git revert --continue</code> or agr code ko delete krna ha to isko use kro.